# Agentforce DX Overview

## Introduction

Agentforce DX provides tools and processes for developing AI-powered agents within Salesforce.

---

## Features

- AI-powered automation
- Natural language interactions
- Salesforce integration
- Custom agent actions
- Workflow automation

---

## Agent Development Process

1. Define business goals
2. Configure data sources
3. Create agent actions
4. Test interactions
5. Deploy and monitor

---

## Benefits

- Increased efficiency
- Better customer experiences
- Reduced manual effort
- Faster problem resolution

---

## Common Use Cases

- Customer service agents
- Sales assistants
- Employee support agents
- Knowledge assistants

---

## Conclusion

Agentforce DX enables developers to build intelligent and scalable AI solutions on Salesforce.
